content:
Salesforce Classic doesn't support mobile browsers, so use the Salesforce mobile app for working on mobile devices. 

Supported browsers:
Microsoft Internet Explorer 11 no longer supported after December 31, 2022
Not supported: Microsoft Edge (non-Chromium), not supported after December 31, 2022
Microsoft Edge Chromium supports latest stable browser version
Google Chrome supports latest stable browser version
Mozilla Firefox supports latest stable browser version
Apple Safari supports latest stable browser version

Salesforce Classic Console:
Supported browsers: Google Chrome, Mozilla Firefox, Apple Safari
Internet Explorer mode for Microsoft Edge Chromium not supported
title: Salesforce Classic Browser Support
